2.text: Each student should have a piece of 15cm x 10 cm Bristol board and colours. Get them to draw a picture. Ask the students to write 'Good Bye' / From… / To…..on the card. Get the students to display the card on the board. Sing the song with the students. Finally ask the students to take their cards and give it to a friend.
